code: public void testNull() {     XContentLocation xContentLocation = new XContentLocation(0, 0).     {         MatchAssertion matchAssertion = new MatchAssertion(xContentLocation, "field", null).         matchAssertion.doAssert(null, null).         expectThrows(AssertionError.class, () -> matchAssertion.doAssert("non-null", null)).     }     {         MatchAssertion matchAssertion = new MatchAssertion(xContentLocation, "field", "non-null").         expectThrows(AssertionError.class, () -> matchAssertion.doAssert(null, "non-null")).     }     {         MatchAssertion matchAssertion = new MatchAssertion(xContentLocation, "field", "/exp/").         expectThrows(AssertionError.class, () -> matchAssertion.doAssert(null, "/exp/")).     } }
